								</g>
								<defs>
									<clipPath id="clip0_1398_3059">
										<rect width="32" height="32" fill="white" transform="translate(4 4)"/>
									</clipPath>
								</defs>
							</svg>
						</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</nav>
		</div>
	 </header>
	 <main class="min-h-[100svh]" id="content">
		<section
			class=
			"h-full min-h-[20rem] w-full py-8 m:py-16 lg:py-[5.25rem] relative overflow-hidden"
			aria-labelledby="about-heading"
			id="about"
		>
			<div class="w-full max-w-[60rem] pxPage mx-auto flex flex-col">
				<h2 class="capitalize tracking-wider w-fit mb-6" id="about-heading">About</h2>
				<p class="max-w-[58ch] font-regular text-xl md:text-2xl mb-12">
					I am a Software Engineer building applications that are fast, easy to use, and do their job.
					<br>
					<br>
					Currently, I am an Associate Research Engineer at <a class="text-primary font-bold transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out hover:text-primary/80 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-accent" href="https://global.abb/group/en/technology/corporate-research-centers/sweden" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" rel="noopener noreferrer">ABB</a>, building monitoring solutions for
					powertrains and machine learning algorithms. I provide solutions to real problems that our
					customers are experiencing in the field.
					<br>
					<br>
					When I am not at my job, I tend to either improve my skills, gym, play piano,
					or hang out with friends.
				</p>
				<div class="flex md:items-center gap-6 flex-col md:flex-row max-w-[40rem]">
					<a href="mailto:r15.hallberg@gmail.com"
					class="bg-primary h-15 rounded-full px-2 w-full
							flex items-center justify-center 
							text-primary-foreground font-bold text-xl
							transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out
							hover:bg-primary/80 focus:outline-none
							focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-accent"
						aria-label="Send email to r15.hallberg@gmail.com">
					Let's Work Together
					</a>
					<CopyEmail />
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section
			class=
			"h-full min-h-[20rem] w-full relative overflow-hidden pb-12"
			aria-labelledby="experience-heading"
			id="experience"
		>
			<div class="w-full max-w-[60rem] pxPage mx-auto flex flex-col">
				<h2 class="capitalize tracking-wider w-fit mb-6" id="experience-heading">Experience</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-12 mb-12">
					{jobs.map(job => (
						<EmploymentItem {...job} />
					))}
				</ul>
				<a href="/Rikard_Hallberg_CV.pdf" class="text-primary font-bold text-xl mb-[-0.4rem]" aria-label="View full Resumé (PDF)">View full Resumé</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	 </main>
	 <footer role="contentinfo" class="w-full max-w-[60rem] pxPage mx-auto flex flex-col">
		<p class="max-w-[52ch]">
			Designed in <a class="text-primary font-bold transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out hover:text-primary/80 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-accent" href="https://www.figma.com/" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" rel="noopener noreferrer">Figma</a>, 
			coded in <a class="text-primary font-bold transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out hover:text-primary/80 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-accent" href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" rel="noopener noreferrer">Visual Studio Code</a> by me. 
			Built with <a class="text-primary font-bold transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out hover:text-primary/80 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-accent" href="https://astro.build/" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a> and
			<a class="text-primary font-bold transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out hover:text-primary/80 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-accent" href="https://tailwindcss.com/" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tailwind CSS</a>, deployed with <a class="text-primary font-bold transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out hover:text-primary/80 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-accent" href="https://pages.cloudflare.com/" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Pages</a>. All text is written in the <a class="text-primary font-bold transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out hover:text-primary/80 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent focus:ring-offset-accent" href="https://typogram.co/font-discovery/how-to-use-poppins-font" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" rel="noopener noreferrer">Poppins</a> typeface.
		</p>
		
	 </footer>
</Layout>
